text: Nguyễn Sỹ Nam (born 7 March 1993) is a Vietnamese footballer who plays as a defender for V-League (Vietnam) club Sông Lam Nghệ An. == References == Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Vietnamese footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:V.League 1 players Category:XSKT Cần Thơ F.C. players Category:Song Lam Nghe An F.C. players
